        <item>
            <title>三排座椅大型電動 SUV   Hyundai IONIQ 9 路測諜照曝光</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/hyundai-ioniq-9-suv-spy-photo-video/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hyundai-ioniq-9-suv-spy-photo-video</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/hyundai-ioniq-9-suv-spy-photo-video/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 05:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Hyundai IONIQ 9]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1272201</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>專門報導電動車消息的網站 Electrek 日前報導，韓國品牌 Hyundai 的大型電動 SUV IONIQ 9 開始在路面實測，並且被媒體拍攝到諜照而提前曝光。高階定位的 IONIQ 9 是 Hyundai 首款擁有三排座椅的電動 SUV，報導還同時提供了新車的內櫳照片，可以見到空間相當充裕。</p><p><span id="more-1272201"></span></p><p>Hyundai IONIQ 9 是基於 2021 年發佈的 SEVEN 概念車，新車將會在 11 月舉行的洛杉磯車展正式發表。IONIQ 9 的外觀設計前衞而獨特，配備具有系列特色的 LED 燈條，還有極具線條感的車身輪廓。雖然無法從諜照知道 IONIQ 9 的實際車身尺寸，但預計會跟 KIA 的 EV9 大型電動 SUV 接近。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_72413"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XU7qQGCX7ZA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>從曝光的內櫳照片可見，IONIQ 9 的第二排腿部空間十分寬敞，估計超過 42 吋，比起競爭對手如 Land Rover 等的空間更加充裕。據悉，IONIQ 9 採用 Hyundai 的 E-GMP 電動車平台，目前已經在 Hyundai 的韓國牙山廠房進行試產，並作最終的質量檢測。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1272217" rel="attachment wp-att-1272217"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272217" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10301b-694x391.jpg" alt="Hyundai IONIQ 9" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10301b-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10301b.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://electrek.co/2024/10/28/hyundai-ioniq-9-spotted-big-body-spacious-interior-images/">electrek</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/28/hyundai-kona-mauna-loa-limited-edition/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">韓國 Hyundai Kona 電動車，越野版 Mauna Loa 日本限量發售</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/17/hyundai-inster-cross-announced/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Hyundai Inster 發表後獲好評，廠方加推户外風格 Cross 版本</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/07/hyundai-inster-price-announcement/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">韓國 Hyundai Inster 電動小車，進軍國際市場售價曝光</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/hyundai-ioniq-9-suv-spy-photo-video/life-tech/auto/">三排座椅大型電動 SUV   Hyundai IONIQ 9 路測諜照曝光</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
